  },
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric current",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "I",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "i",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-1-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-1-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity equal to the quotient of the net quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) electric charge stem:[\"d\"Q] (<<t6-2.1>>) transferred through a surface during a quasi-infinitesimal time interval and the duration stem:[\"d\"t] of that interval:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nI = (\"d\"Q)/(\"d\"t)\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Electric current is one of the base quantities in the International System of Quantities, ISQ, on which the International System of Units, SI, is based.\n\nElectric current stem:[I] through a surface stem:[\"S\"] can also be written as\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nI = int_\"S\" bb(ii(J)) * e_\"n\" \"d\"A\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(J))] is the electric current density (<<t6-8>>) and where stem:[e_\"n\" \"d\"A] is the vector surface element.\n\nElectric current produces a magnetic field.\n\nFor related definitions, see <<t6-8>> and <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-13\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-2.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-2.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Q",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-2.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "q",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-2.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-2.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-2.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-2.1-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-2.1-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "additive scalar quantity attributed to any particle and, generally, any system of them, to characterize its electromagnetic interactions",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "To denote a point charge, stem:[q] is often used, as is done in this document.\n\nElectromagnetic interactions are Coulomb-Lorentz forces, see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-20\">>.\n\nThe coherent SI unit of charge is coulomb, stem:[\"unitsml(C)\"]. Another frequently used unit is the ampere-hour (stem:[\"unitsml(A*h)\"]) mentioned in <<iec60050-313,locality:item=\"313-01-16\">>, widely used for battery characteristics.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A*s"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-2.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "elementary charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-2.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "e",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-2.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-2.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-2.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-2.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "magnitude of the negative electric charge carried by a single electron, which has charge stem:[-1 e]",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "In the SI system the elementary charge, stem:[e], is one of the fundamental constants with an exact value\n\nstem:[e = 1.602176634 xx 10^(-19) \"unitsml(C)\"], see <<bipm-si>>.\n\nElectric charge can be positive, negative or zero. The sign convention is such that the elementary electric charge, stem:[e], of the proton, is positive. See <<iec60050-113,locality:item=\"113-02-12\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A*s"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric charge density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-3-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "volumic electric charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-3-2",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "volumic charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "rho",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-3",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-3",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-3-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-3-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-3-2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-3-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity representing the spatial distribution of electric charge,\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nrho(bb(ii(r))) = (\"d\"Q)/(\"d\"V)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[\"d\"Q] is quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) electric charge (<<t6-2.1>>) contained in a quasi-infinitesimal 3D domain located at position stem:[bb(ii(r))] and stem:[\"d\"V] is quasi-infinitesimal volume (<<iso80000-3>>) of this domain\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-07\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C/m^3"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^(-3)*s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-4-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "surface density of electric charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-4-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "areic electric charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-4-2",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "areic charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-4-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "sigma",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-4",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-4",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-4-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-4-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-4-2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-4-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity representing the areal distribution of electric charge,\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nsigma = sigma(r) = (\"d\"Q)/(\"d\"A)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[\"d\"Q] is a quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) electric charge (<<t6-2.1>>) contained in a quasi-infinitesimal 2D domain located at position stem:[r], and stem:[\"d\"A] is a quasi-infinitesimal area (<<iso80000-3>>) of this domain\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-08\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^-2*s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-5-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "linear density of electric charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-5-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "lineic electric charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-5-2",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "lineic charge",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-5-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "tau",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-5",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-5",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-5-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-5-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-5-2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-5-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity representing the linear distribution of electric charge,\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\ntau = tau(bb(ii(r))) = (\"d\"Q)/(\"d\"l)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[\"d\"Q] is a quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) electric charge (<<t6-2.1>>) contained in a quasi-infinitesimal domain located at position stem:[bb(ii(r))] and stem:[\"d\"l] is a quasi-infinitesimal length (<<iso80000-3>>) of this domain\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-09\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^-1*s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-6-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric dipole moment",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-6-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "p",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-6",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-6",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-6-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-6-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-6-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\np = q(r_\"+\" - r_\"-\")\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[r_\"+\"] and stem:[r_\"-\"] are the position vectors (<<iso80000-3>>) of the carriers of electric charges stem:[q] and stem:[-q] (<<t6-2.1>>), respectively\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The electric dipole moment of a substance within a domain is the vector sum of electric dipole moments of all electric dipoles contained in the domain.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-35\";and!locality:item=\"121-11-36\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C*m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m*s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-7-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric polarization",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-7-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "P",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-7",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-7",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-7-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-7-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity representing the spatial distribution of electric dipole moment,\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nP(bb(ii(r))) = (\"d\"p)/(\"d\"V)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[\"d\"p] is quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) electric dipole moment (<<t6-6>>) of a substance in a quasi-infinitesimal domain at position stem:[bb(ii(r))] and stem:[\"d\"V] is quasi-infinitesimal volume (<<iso80000-3>>) of this domain\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-37\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^-2*s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-8-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric current density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-8-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(J))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-8",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-8",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-8-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-8-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-8-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity equal to the sum, for the charge carriers within a volume element of quasi-infinitesimal volume stem:[V], of the products of their electric charge stem:[Q_i] and their velocity stem:[sf(ii(v))_i], divided by the volume stem:[V], given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(J))(bb(ii(r))) = bb(ii(J)) = rho sf(ii(v))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[i] is the rank of the charge carrier\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "There can be different charge carriers with different velocities.\n\nElectric current stem:[I] (<<t6-1>>) through a surface stem:[\"S\"] is\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nI = int_\"S\" bb(ii(J)) e_\"n\" \"d\"A\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[e_\"n\" \"d\"A] is the vector surface element.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-11\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^(-2)*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-9-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "linear electric current density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-9-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(J))_\"S\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-9",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-9",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-9-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-9-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity equal to the sum, for the charge carriers confined to a surface element of quasi-infinitesimal area stem:[\"S\"], of the products of their electric charge stem:[Q_i] and their velocity stem:[sf(ii(v))_i], divided by the area stem:[\"S\"]\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(J))_\"S\"(bb(ii(r))) = bb(ii(J))_\"S\" = sigma sf(ii(v))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[i] is the rank of the charge carrier\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-12\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^-1*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-10-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric field strength",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-10-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(E))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-10",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-10",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-10-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-10-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "additive vector field quantity that exerts on any charged particle located at position stem:[bb(ii(r))] a force stem:[bb(ii(F))] (<<iso80000-4>>) equal to the product of stem:[E] and electric charge stem:[q] (<<t6-2.1>>) of the particle, thus:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(E))(bb(ii(r))) = bb(ii(F))/q\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-18\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-V/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m*s^(-3)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric potential",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "V",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "varphi",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-11.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-11.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.1-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.1-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity expressed by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\n-bb(\"grad\") V = bb(ii(E)) + (del bb(ii(A)))/(del t)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(E))] is electric field strength (<<t6-10>>), stem:[bb(ii(A))] is magnetic vector potential (<<t6-32>>) and stem:[t] is time (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The electric potential is not unique since any constant scalar field quantity can be added to it without changing its gradient.\n\nThe electric potential, the electric field, and the magnetic vector potential depend on the position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-25\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-V"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-3)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric potential difference",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "V_\"ab\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-11.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-11.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nV_\"ab\" = V_\"a\" - V_\"b\"\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[V_\"a\"] and stem:[V_\"b\"] are the electric potentials (<<t6-11.1>>) at points stem:[\"a\"] and stem:[\"b\"], respectively\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nV_\"ab\" = int_(bb(ii(r))_\"a\"(C))^(bb(ii(r))_\"b\") (bb(ii(E)) + (del bb(ii(A)))/(del t)) \"d\"bb(ii(r))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(E))] is electric field strength (<<t6-10>>), stem:[bb(ii(A))] is magnetic vector potential (<<t6-32>>), stem:[t] is time (<<iso80000-3>>), and stem:[bb(ii(r))] is the position vector (<<iso80000-3>>) along a given curve stem:[\"C\"], from point stem:[\"a\"] to point stem:[\"b\"].\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-26\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-V"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-3)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "voltage",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.3-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric tension",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "U",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.3-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "U_\"ab\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.3-2",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "u",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-11.3",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-11.3",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.3-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.3-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.3-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.3-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.3-2"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for a conductor, scalar quantity given by the electric potential difference stem:[V_\"ab\"] (<<t6-11.2>>) between two points stem:[\"a\"] and stem:[\"b\"] respectively",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The name \"voltage\", commonly used in the English language, is given in the IEV, but it is an exception to the principle that a quantity name should not refer to any name of a unit.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-27\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-V"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-3)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.4-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "induced voltage",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.4-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "U_i",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-11.4",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-11.4",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-11.4-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-11.4-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "negative of time derivative of protoflux (<<t6-22.2>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nU_i = -\"d\"/(\"d\"t) int_\"C\" bb(ii(A)) * \"d\"bb(ii(r))\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "If the integration path is closed, the loop voltage is\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nU_\"l\" = -\"d\"/(\"d\"t) oint_\"C\" bb(ii(A)) * \"d\"bb(ii(r)) = - (\"d\"Phi)/(\"d\"t)\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-V"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-3)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-12-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric flux density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-12-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric displacement",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-12-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(D))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-12",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-12",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-12-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-12-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-12-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(D)) = epsilon_0 bb(ii(E)) + bb(ii(P))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[epsilon_0] is electric constant (<<t6-14.1>>), stem:[bb(ii(E))] is electric field strength (<<t6-10>>), and stem:[bb(ii(P))] is electric polarization (<<t6-7>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The electric flux density is related to electric charge density via stem:[bb(\"div\") bb(ii(D)) = rho] where stem:[bb(\"div\")] denotes divergence.\n\nThe electric flux density, the electric field strength, and the polarization depend on the position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-40\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^-2*s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-13-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "capacitance",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-13-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "C",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-13",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-13",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-13-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-13-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for a capacitive element, quotient of electric charge stem:[Q] and voltage stem:[U] (<<t6-11.3>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nC = Q/U\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The electric charge of a capacitive element is given by the time integral of the electric current.\n\nSee <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-11\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-F"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg^(-1)*m^(-2)*s^4*A^2"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-14.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric constant",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-14.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "permittivity of vacuum",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-14.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "epsilon_0",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-14.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-14.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-14.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-14.1-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-14.1-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nepsilon_0 = 1/(mu_0 c_0^2)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[mu_0] is the magnetic constant (<<t6-26.1>>) and stem:[c_0] is luminal speed (<<t6-35.2>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-03\">>.\n\nThis quantity is considered to be constant in time.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-F/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg^(-1)*m^(-3)*s^4*A^2"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-14.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "permittivity",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-14.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "epsilon",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-14.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-14.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-14.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-14.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for linear media, proportionality constant between electric flux density stem:[bb(ii(D))] (<<t6-12>>) and electric field strength stem:[bb(ii(E))] (<<t6-10>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(D)) = epsilon bb(ii(E))\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Permittivity stem:[epsilon] is a property of a medium. For an inhomogeneous medium, permittivity stem:[epsilon] depends on position.\n\nFor an isotropic medium, stem:[epsilon] is a scalar quantity; for an anisotropic medium, stem:[epsilon] is a second-order tensor.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-12\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-F/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg^(-1)*m^(-3)*s^4*A^2"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-15-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "relative permittivity",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-15-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "epsilon_\"r\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-15",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-15",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-15-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-15-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for linear media, quotient of permittivity stem:[epsilon] (<<t6-14.2>>) and the electric constant stem:[epsilon_0] (<<t6-14.1>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nepsilon_\"r\" = epsilon/epsilon_0\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-13\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-16-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric susceptibility",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-16-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "chi",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-16",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-16",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-16-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-16-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for linear media, scalar quantity expressed by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(P)) = epsilon_0 chi bb(ii(E))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(P))] is electric polarization (<<t6-7>>), stem:[epsilon_0] is the electric constant (<<t6-14.1>>), and stem:[bb(ii(E))] is electric field strength (<<t6-10>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[chi = epsilon_r - 1] where stem:[epsilon_r] is relative permittivity (<<t6-15>>)\n\nElectric susceptibility stem:[chi] is a property of a medium. For an inhomogeneous medium, electric susceptibility stem:[chi] depends on position.\n\nFor an isotropic medium, stem:[chi] is a scalar quantity; for an anisotropic medium, stem:[chi] is a second order tensor.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-19\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-17-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electric flux",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-17-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "psi",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-17",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-17",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-17-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-17-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the integral\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\npsi = int_\"S\" bb(ii(D)) * e_\"n\" \"d\"A\n++++\n\nover a surface stem:[\"S\"], where stem:[bb(ii(D))] is electric flux density (<<t6-12>>) and stem:[e_\"n\"\"d\"A] is a vector surface element (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-41\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-C"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-s*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-18-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "displacement current density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-18-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(J))_\"D\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-18",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-18",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-18-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-18-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(J))_\"D\" = (del bb(ii(D)))/(del t)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(D))] is electric flux density (<<t6-12>>) and stem:[t] is time (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-42\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^(-2)*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-19.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "displacement current",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-19.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "I_\"D\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-19.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-19.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-19.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-19.1-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the integral\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nI_\"D\" = int_\"S\" bb(ii(J))_\"D\" * e_\"n\" \"d\"A\n++++\n\nover a surface stem:[\"S\"], where stem:[bb(ii(J))_\"D\"] is displacement current density (<<t6-18>>) and stem:[e_\"n\" \"d\"A] is a vector surface element (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-43\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-19.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "total current",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-19.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "I_\"tot\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-19.2-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "I_\"t\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-19.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-19.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-19.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-19.2-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-19.2-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the sum of electric current stem:[I] (<<t6-1>>) and displacement current stem:[I_\"D\"] (<<t6-19.1>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nI_\"tot\" = I + I_\"D\"\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-45\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-20-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "total current density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-20-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(J))_\"tot\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-20-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(J))_\"t\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-20",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-20",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-20-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-20-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-20-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by the sum of electric current density stem:[bb(ii(J))] (<<t6-8>>) and displacement current density stem:[bb(ii(J))_\"D\"] (<<t6-18>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(J))_\"tot\" = bb(ii(J)) + bb(ii(J))_\"D\"\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121:1998,locality:item=\"121-11-44\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^(-2)*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-21-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic flux density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-21-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(B))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-21",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-21",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-21-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-21-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity expressed by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(F)) = q sf(ii(v)) xx bb(ii(B))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(F))] is the force (<<iso80000-4>>) acting on a test particle with electric charge stem:[q] (<<t6-2.1>>) traversing a magnetic field with flux density stem:[bb(ii(B))], with velocity stem:[sf(ii(v))] (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The magnetic flux density depends on position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-19\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-T"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic flux",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Phi",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-22.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-22.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.1-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.1-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the integral\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nPhi = int_\"S\" bb(ii(B))*e_\"n\" \"d\"A\n++++\n\nover a surface stem:[\"S\"], where stem:[bb(ii(B))] is magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>) and stem:[e_\"n\" \"d\"A] is a vector surface element (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Magnetic flux can also be given by the line integral of the magnetic vector potential stem:[A], (<<t6-32>>) over a closed curve stem:[\"C\"] which is the border of area stem:[\"S\"]:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nPhi = oint_\"C\" A \"d\"r\n++++\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-21\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Wb"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "protoflux",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Psi_\"p\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-22.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-22.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the integral\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nPsi_\"p\" = int_\"C\" A*\"d\"r\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[A] is magnetic vector potential (<<t6-32>>) and stem:[\"d\"r] is a line vector element of the path stem:[\"C\"]\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The former name \"linked flux\" is deprecated.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-24\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Wb"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "linked magnetic flux",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Phi_\"l\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-22.3",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-22.3",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.3-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.3-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "magnetic flux (<<t6-22.1>>), the integration surface of which is such that magnetic field lines cross it in the same orientation more than once",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-24\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Wb"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.4-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "total magnetic flux",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.4-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Psi",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.4-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Phi_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-22.4",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-22.4",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-22.4-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.4-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-22.4-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "highest value of the magnetic flux (<<t6-22.1>>) produced by a current loop",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The integration surface for the magnetic flux has to be chosen such that it is crossed in the same direction by all magnetic field lines produced by the current loop.\n\nThe total flux can be a linked flux (<<t6-22.3>>).\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Wb"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-23-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic moment",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-23-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic area moment",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-23-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "m",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-23",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-23",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-23-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-23-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-23-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "additive vector quantity, for a quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) planar loop given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nm = I e_\"n\" A\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[I] is the electric current (<<t6-1>>) in a loop, stem:[e_\"n\"] is a unit vector perpendicular to the planar surface stem:[\"S\"] enclosed by the loop, and stem:[A] is the area (<<iso80000-3>>) in the loop\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "A magnetic moment is associated with systems of charged particles, such as atoms, molecules, atomic nuclei, nucleons. It can be considered as a product of the motion of charged particles and the magnetic moments of these particles.\n\nMagnetic moment is also an intrinsic property of any charged elementary particle with half-integer spin (e.g. an electron, a neutron or a quark).\n\nThe magnetic moment of a substance within a domain is the vector sum of the magnetic moments of all entities contained in the domain.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-49\";and!locality:item=\"121-11-50\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A*m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^2*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-24-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetization",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-24-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(M))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-24-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(H_\"i\"))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-24",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-24",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-24-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-24-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-24-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity representing the spatial distribution of the magnetic moment,\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(M))(bb(ii(r))) = (\"d\"m)/(\"d\"V)\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[\"d\"m] is quasi-infinitesimal (see <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-06\">>) magnetic moment (<<t6-23>>) of a substance contained in a 3D domain located at position stem:[bb(ii(r))], and stem:[\"d\"V] is volume (<<iso80000-3>>) of this domain\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-52\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^(-1)*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-25-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic field strength",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-25-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetizing field",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-25-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(H))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-25",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-25",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-25-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-25-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-25-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(H)) = bb(ii(B))/mu_0 - bb(ii(M))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(B))] is magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>), stem:[mu_0] is the magnetic constant (<<t6-26.1>>), and stem:[bb(ii(M))] is the magnetization (<<t6-24>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The magnetic field strength is related to the total current density stem:[bb(ii(J))_\"tot\"] (<<t6-20>>) via\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(rot) bb(ii(H)) = bb(ii(J))_\"tot\"\n++++\n\nThe magnetic field strength, the magnetic flux density, and the magnetization depend on the position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-56\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^(-1)*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-26.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic constant",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-26.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "permeability of vacuum",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-26.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "mu_0",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-26.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-26.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-26.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-26.1-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-26.1-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by\nstem:[mu_0 ~~ 4pi xx 10^(-7) \"unitsml(H/m)\"] with a relative standard uncertainty of stem:[2.3 xx 10^(-10)]\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "This quantity is considered to be constant in time.\n\nThe numerical value of the magnetic constant was originally exactly stem:[4pi xx 10^(-7)]. It must be determined experimentally; see <<bipm-si>>.\n\nSee <<bipm-si>> and <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-14\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-H/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m*s^(-2)*A^(-2)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-26.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "permeability",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-26.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "mu",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-26.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-26.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-26.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-26.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for linear media, proportionality constant between magnetic flux density stem:[bb(ii(B))] (<<t6-21>>) and magnetic field strength stem:[bb(ii(H))] (<<t6-25>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(B)) = mu bb(ii(H))\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Permeability stem:[mu] is a property of a medium. For an inhomogeneous medium, permeability stem:[mu] depends on position. For an isotropic medium, stem:[mu] is a scalar quantity; for an anisotropic medium, stem:[mu] is a second order tensor.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-28\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-H/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m*s^(-2)*A^(-2)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-27-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "relative permeability",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-27-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "mu_\"r\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-27",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-27",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-27-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-27-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for linear media, quotient of permeability stem:[mu] (<<t6-26.2>>) and the magnetic constant stem:[mu_0] (<<t6-26.1>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nmu_\"r\" = mu/mu_0\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-29\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-28-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic susceptibility",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-28-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "kappa",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-28-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "chi_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-28",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-28",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-28-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-28-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-28-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for linear media, proportionality constant between magnetization stem:[M] (<<t6-24>>) and magnetic field strength stem:[H] (<<t6-25>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nM = kappa H\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[kappa = mu_\"r\" - 1] where stem:[mu_r] is relative permeability (<<t6-27>>).\n\nThis definition applies to an isotropic medium. For an anisotropic medium, magnetic susceptibility is a second order tensor.\n\nThe magnetization and the magnetic field strength depend on position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-37\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-29-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic polarization",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-29-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "J_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-29",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-29",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-29-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-29-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by the product of the magnetic constant stem:[mu_0] (<<t6-26.1>>) and magnetization stem:[M] (<<t6-24>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nJ_\"m\" = mu_0 M\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-54\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-T"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Wb/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-30-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic dipole moment",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-30-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "j_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-30-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "j",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-30",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-30",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-30-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-30-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-30-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by the product of the magnetic constant stem:[mu_0] (<<t6-26.1>>) and magnetic moment stem:[m] (<<t6-23>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nj_\"m\" = mu_0 m\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-55\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-Wb*m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^3*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-31-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "coercivity",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-31-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "coercive field strength",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-31-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "H_\"c\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-31",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-31",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-31-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-31-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-31-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity giving the magnetic field strength (<<t6-25>>) to be applied to bring the magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>) in a substance from its remanent magnetic flux density to zero",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-69\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A/m"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m^-1*A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-32-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic vector potential",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-32-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(A))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-32",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-32",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-32-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-32-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity expressed by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(B)) = bb(rot) bb(ii(A))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(B))] is magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The magnetic vector potential is not unique since any irrotational vector field can be added to it without changing its rotation.\n\nThe magnetic vector potential and the magnetic flux density depend on position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-23\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-J/(A*m)"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m*s^(-2)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-33-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "electromagnetic energy density",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-33-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "w",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-33",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-33",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-33-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-33-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the sum of scalar products:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nw = (1//2)(bb(ii(E)) * bb(ii(D)) + bb(ii(B)) * bb(ii(H)))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(E))] is electric field strength (<<t6-10>>), stem:[bb(ii(D))] is electric flux density (<<t6-12>>), stem:[bb(ii(B))] is magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>), and stem:[bb(ii(H))] is magnetic field strength (<<t6-25>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Electromagnetic energy is a special kind of energy (<<iso80000-5>>). The electromagnetic energy density depends on position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-65\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-J/m^3"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^(-1)*s^(-2)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-34-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "Poynting vector",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-34-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "bb(ii(S))",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-34",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-34",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-34-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-34-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "vector quantity given by the vector product\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(S)) = bb(ii(E)) xx bb(ii(H))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(E))] is electric field strength (<<t6-10>>) and stem:[bb(ii(H))] is magnetic field strength (<<t6-25>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The Poynting vector depends on the position.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-66\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-W/m^2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*s^-3"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "phase speed of electromagnetic waves",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-35.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "c",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-35.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-35.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-35.1-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the quotient of angular frequency stem:[omega] (<<iso80000-3>>) and angular wavenumber stem:[k] (<<iso80000-3>>) in a given direction:\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nc=omega/k\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iso80000-3>>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m/s"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m*s^-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "speed of light in vacuum",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.2-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "light speed in vacuum",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.2-2",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "luminal speed",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-35.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "c_0",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-35.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-35.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.2-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-35.2-2"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-35.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity equal to the speed of electromagnetic waves in vacuum (<<iso80000-1>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nc_0 = 299792458 \"unitsml(m/s)\"\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "This value is not only valid for electromagnetic waves in vacuum, but also for gravitational waves. It is also the upper limit for the speed of propagation of information since this requires a physical carrier. This quantity is considered to be constant in time.\n\nIts value has been fixed by CGMP (see <<bipm-si>>).\n\nSee also <<iec60050-113,locality:item=\"113-01-34\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m/s"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-m*s^-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-36-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "source voltage",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-36-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "source tension",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-36-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "U_\"s\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-36",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-36",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-36-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-36-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-36-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "voltage (<<t6-11.3>>) between the two terminals of an electric source when there is no electric current (<<t6-1>>) through the source",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The name \"electromotive force\" with the abbreviated term EMF, and the symbol stem:[E] are deprecated.\nSee <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-22\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-V"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-3)*A^(-1)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-37.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic potential",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "V_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "varphi",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-37.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-37.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-37.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.1-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.1-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for an irrotational magnetic field strength, scalar quantity expressed by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nbb(ii(H)) = -bb(\"grad\") V_\"m\"\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(H))] is magnetic field strength (<<t6-25>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The magnetic scalar potential is not unique since any constant scalar field can be added to it without changing its gradient.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-58\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-37.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetic tension",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "U_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-37.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-37.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-37.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "in a magnetic field strength, scalar quantity given by the line integral along a given curve stem:[\"C\"] from point stem:[\"a\"] to point stem:[\"b\"];\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nU_\"m\" = int_(bb(ii(r))_\"a\"(\"C\"))^(bb(ii(r))_\"b\") bb(ii(H)) * \"d\"bb(ii(r))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(H))] is magnetic field strength (<<t6-25>>) and stem:[bb(ii(r))] is position vector (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "For an irrotational magnetic field strength, this quantity is equal to the magnetic potential difference.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-57\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-37.3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "magnetomotive force",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.3-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "F_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-37.3",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-37.3",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-37.3-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-37.3-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the line integral along a closed curve stem:[\"C\"];\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nF_\"m\" = oint_\"C\" bb(ii(H)) * \"d\"bb(ii(r))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[bb(ii(H))] is magnetic field strength (<<t6-25>>) and stem:[bb(ii(r))] is position vector (<<iso80000-3>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Compare to the remark in <<t6-36>>.\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-11-60\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-A"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-38-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "number of turns in a winding",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-38-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "N",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-38",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-38",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-38-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-38-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-38-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "<in winding> number of turns",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "stem:[N] may be a non-integer number, see <<iso80000-3>>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-39-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "reluctance",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-39-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "R_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-39-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "R",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-39",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-39",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-39-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-39-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-39-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the quotient of magnetic tension stem:[U_\"m\"] (<<t6-37.2>>) and total magnetic flux stem:[Psi] (<<t6-22.4>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nR_\"m\" = (U_\"m\")/Psi\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-28\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-H^(-1)"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg^(-1)*m^(-2)*s^2*A^2"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-40-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "permeance",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-40-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "ii(Lambda)",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-40",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-40",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-40-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-40-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by the inverse of reluctance stem:[R_\"m\"] (<<t6-39>>);\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nii(Lambda) = 1/R_\"m\"\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-29\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-H"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-2)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-41.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "inductance",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-41.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "self-inductance",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-41.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "L",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-41.1-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "L_\"m\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-41.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-41.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-41.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-41.1-1"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-41.1-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-41.1-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "scalar quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nL=Psi/I\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[Psi] is the total magnetic flux (<<t6-22.4>>) in a conducting loop caused by the magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>) produced by the electric current stem:[I] (<<t6-1>>) in that loop\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "The name \"self-inductance\" is used for the quantity associated with mutual inductance when stem:[n = m].\n\nSee <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-19\">> and <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-35\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-H"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-2)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-41.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "mutual inductance",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-41.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "L_\"mn\"",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-41.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-41.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-41.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-41.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for thin conducting loops (numbered stem:[m], stem:[n]), scalar quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nL_\"mn\" = Phi_\"m\"/I_\"n\"\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[Phi_\"m\"] is the total magnetic flux (<<t6-22.4>>) in a loop stem:[\"m\"], caused by the magnetic flux density (<<t6-21>>) produced by the electric current stem:[I_\"n\"] (<<t6-1>>) in another loop stem:[\"n\"]\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nL_\"mn\" = L_\"nm\"\n++++\n\nSee <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-36\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-H"
        },
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-kg*m^2*s^(-2)*A^(-2)"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-42.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "coupling factor",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-42.1-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "k",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-42.1",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-42.1",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-42.1-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-42.1-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for inductive coupling between two inductive elements (numbered stem:[\"m\"], stem:[\"n\"]), scalar quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nk = (abs(L_(\"mn\")))/(sqrt(L_\"m\"L_\"n\"))\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[L_\"m\"] and stem:[L_\"n\"] are their self-inductances (<<t6-41.1>>), and stem:[L_\"mn\"] is their mutual inductance (<<t6-41.2>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-41\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-42.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "leakage factor",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-42.2-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "sigma",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-42.2",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-42.2",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-42.2-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-42.2-0"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "for inductive coupling between two inductive elements, scalar quantity given by\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nsigma = 1 - k^2\n++++\n\nwhere stem:[k] is the coupling factor (<<t6-42.1>>)\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "See <<iec60050-131,locality:item=\"131-12-42\">>.",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
          "@id": "isoiec80000:unit-1"
        }
      ],
      "smart:hasBindingnessType": {
        "@id": "smart:normative"
      },
      "dcterms:isPartOf": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/part-6"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-43-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "conductivity",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:fullForm"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-43-0",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "sigma",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-43-1",
      "@type": [
        "smart:Term",
        "skosxl:Label"
      ],
      "skosxl:literalForm": {
        "@value": "kappa",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "smart:hasTermFormType": {
        "@id": "smart:symbol"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/t6-43",
      "@type": [
        "isoiec80000:Quantity",
        "smart:TermEntry"
      ],
      "dcterms:identifier": "6-43",
      "skosxl:prefLabel": {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/term-t6-43-0"
      },
      "skosxl:altLabel": [
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-43-0"
        },
        {
          "@id": "https://w3id.org/standards/isoiec80000/ontologies/core/sym-t6-43-1"
        }
      ],
      "skos:definition": {
        "@value": "proportionality factor between electric current density stem:[J] (<<t6-8>>) and electric field strength stem:[E] (<<t6-10>>)\n\n[stem%unnumbered]\n++++\nJ = sigma E\n++++\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "skos:note": {
        "@value": "Conductivity stem:[sigma] is a property of a medium. For an inhomogeneous medium, conductivity stem:[sigma] depends on position. For an isotropic medium, stem:[sigma] is a scalar quantity; for an anisotropic medium, stem:[sigma] is a second-order tensor.\n\nThe symbol stem:[kappa] is used in electrochemistry (see <<iso80000-9>>).\n\nSee <<iec60050-121,locality:item=\"121-12-03\">>.\n",
        "@language": "en"
      },
      "isoiec80000:hasUnit": [
        {
